cs.HC, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.CYBER, cs.CE

This paper focuses on the design and evaluation of an emotion-aware chatbot for health/wellness applications, which involves aspects of human-computer interaction (cs.HC), natural language processing (cs.CL), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the potential use of the chatbot in mHealth contexts, which could fall under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CYBER) or computer engineering (cs.CE).
